The level 2 modeling is responsible for extracting the clinical features for each line list case. Extraction of clinical features is a binary classification problem where we have to classify each feature into two classes - Y or N. The first phase of level 2 modeling is similar to level 1 modeling. Seed indicator for each clinical feature is provided as input to the level 2 modeling and
